  <section>
    <title>RFCs</title>
    <para>
      Request for Comments (RFC) are draft proposals to which other developers
      can comment. After a while, RFCs are converted into standards which
      will be preceded by a Call for Votes (CFV). During a period of time
      developers can vote YES/NO on the RFC. If the majority votes in favor
      of the RFC, it will be accepted.
    </para>
